{"product_id":"nurme-lavender-hair-conditioner-250ml","title":"NURME Lavender Conditioner 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eOur all-natural hair conditioners are rich in fatty acids and have a smoothing and moisturizing quality. It gives your hair shine and makes it softer to the touch. The conditioner gives a protective coating to the air follicles and therefor preventing hair breakage.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLavender essential oil is richly nourishing, moisturizes the scalp and hair, helps prevent hair loss, and improves scalp circulation, thereby promoting hair growth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eAfter washing add a small amount of conditioner to your hair and leave it on for 1-2 minutes. For extra nourishment, gently massage some product on the scalp. Rinse with plenty of water.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eThe conditioner is very thick which means it doesn’t take much. When the bottle is emptied to the last third, we recommend to add a little water to facilitate use.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetyl Alcohol**, Glycerin**, Behentrimonium Chloride*, Betaine**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil*, Panthenol*, Tocopherol**, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Flower Oil*, Behenyl Alcohol**, Decyltetradecanol*, Sodium Benzoate**, Oleyl Erucate**, Potassium Sorbate**, Citric Acid, Linalool***. \u003cem\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e*Natural origin **Natural products approved ingredients ***Occures naturally in essential oils\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e0% SLS | 0% SLES | 0% Parabens\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49553876746567,"sku":null,"price":11.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-lavender-conditioner-250ml-812234.jpg?v=1739897248","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/nurme-lavender-hair-conditioner-250ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}